c: 48
v: 29
t: "UMuhammad nguMthunywa ka-Allâh ukanti abo bakunye naye bangqwabalala kwabangakholwayo, banenceba phakathi kwabo (bodwa). Ubabona bequbuda (emthandazweni) befuna ubuBele buka-Allâh nokuthandwa nguYe. Uphawu lwabo lusebusweni babo (emabunzini) oluvela kumzila wokuqubuda. Yinkcazo yabo ke leyo ephuma kwiTorah, kanti inkcazo yabo kwiVangeli injengesityalo esivelisa iingcambu zaso, size sizomeleze ukuze zintshule ziqine zime ngeziqu zazo, zivuyise umlimi (wazo) khona ukuze (uAllâh) Abahlahlambise abangakholwayo. UAllâh Uthembise abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo ezilungileyo phakathi kwabo, ngoxolelo lwezono, nomvuzo omkhulu"